{"id": 1778, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于如何在社交网络上显得比较酷，你都有哪些心得？", "description": "你都如何在社交网络上表现你清奇的品格和别致的气息？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3224, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170703171147J91hqmAw6TvW7rg3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-31T03:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 226304, "content": "自己没有牛逼的东东拿出来，就先看看别人的牛逼展现吧?！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008028}, {"id": 239616, "content": "要么不发朋友圈要么发有自己风格的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541113}, {"id": 226049, "content": "展现出大量的原则般的自律、克制以及底蕴，比如发图只发1、3、6或9张，转发前必点赞的自定的“礼仪”，评论与私密评论同时用的双面性，话题不局限并且有深度，用词丰富多样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226305, "content": "使用小众的产品 并习以为常 偶尔外出旅游 用所谓惊世骇俗的语气揭露一些很理所当然的东西 -", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001220}, {"id": 227073, "content": "各位莘莘学子，各位辛劳的妈妈们，还有各位办公室人员，不管您是哪种身份，只要您有空余的时 间，那么这份工作一定适合您【日挣100--200块钱】， 别再犹豫喽，赶快卫鑫:yy236697", "image": "img/option/option/20170803223228xuZ6EBHjfU3tJ0Vw", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095526}, {"id": 226050, "content": "好像大家都在谈怎么装逼?", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580270}, {"id": 226306, "content": "说的话不和别人一样语气，发的照片不和别人一样套路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852030}, {"id": 226562, "content": "只分享好奇心日报的文章。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746201}, {"id": 232706, "content": "一文不发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119251}, {"id": 226051, "content": "不跟风 保持自我", "image": "img/option/option/20170731114525TahjMoXIznq7bri2.jpg", "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093014}, {"id": 226052, "content": "什么都不发(´∀｀)σ", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643616}, {"id": 226053, "content": "将社交网络上自带的功能用得自然流畅随心所欲炉火纯青神哭鬼泣天地变色，展现出对工具的高超的使用艺术和控制力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226309, "content": "有sns但极少更新", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522195}, {"id": 226054, "content": "出去旅游九张风景照一波A上去，什么也不说，标签上默默地当个定位。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083622}, {"id": 226310, "content": "装逼的境界比别人都高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023121}, {"id": 226055, "content": "坚持做一件相同的事，并记录下来，这本身就不容易。", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091831}, {"id": 226311, "content": "如果我不在这里发表，是不是会更酷？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093509}, {"id": 226056, "content": "虽然多数人的生活很枯燥，但是你可能很丰富，此外你可能有牢骚，可是，请挑选至多三条最重要的发出来，并且过后迅速删除仅保留最重要的留待他人翻看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226312, "content": "不发旅游照\n不发定位\n不晒美食\n不分享歌曲\n不转发文章\n不发好看的自拍\n超酷der", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652118}, {"id": 226057, "content": "内心深深的认为，老子最酷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847203}, {"id": 226313, "content": "你们都不懂我的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093757}, {"id": 226058, "content": "不自拍，不轻易发生活照\n从不轻易点赞评论\n看心情发一些，但时间间隔不要太短。\n最后真的就做自己，开心呢就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949545}, {"id": 226314, "content": "不为了装逼而故作高冷小众：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697470}, {"id": 226570, "content": "不进入网络社交", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093906}, {"id": 226826, "content": "不去在意别人的评论，发自己想发的，随心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095502}, {"id": 226059, "content": "别刻意去考虑如何让自己比较酷→_→没事装逼看起来就像个。。。那啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042633}, {"id": 226315, "content": "在朋友圈消失的无影无踪，偶尔会来个高逼格音乐或者一张照片，不发表任何文字……然后再消失", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749950}, {"id": 226060, "content": "少发照片。尤其不要发你觉得好看/美的照片，因为那很可能并不美。好玩的也要克制，不达到“日式冷吐槽”的水准不要发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226316, "content": "真正酷炫的人无需扮酷，他就是酷。真正牛逼的人无需装逼，他就是逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 226061, "content": "少抖机灵/激灵。不接近“好奇心辞典”的水准不要发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226317, "content": "分享一些在自己知识圈外的神秘技能，会感觉很酷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613298}, {"id": 227085, "content": "酷就是酷，装出来有意思么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096137}, {"id": 226062, "content": "反正就是神秘感就对了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093018}, {"id": 226063, "content": "少讨好粉丝或好友。不达到好奇心日报的迂回讨好年青人的境界不要讨好（滑稽", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226065, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092212}, {"id": 226066, "content": "含蓄深刻的讽刺，发自内心的幽默", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226067, "content": "你以为的酷其实没人在乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 272, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603974}, {"id": 226068, "content": "成为或就是一个酷的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 226324, "content": "天然独特", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044812}, {"id": 226069, "content": "不发朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091824}, {"id": 226325, "content": "不矫情\n不八卦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093820}, {"id": 226326, "content": "写一首特别特别文艺的诗，里面要包含徐志摩，林徽因的句子，最后发表在朋友圈里。\n赢得无数的赞与评论。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015172}, {"id": 226838, "content": "显得酷，没有真正的酷来的爽！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787171}, {"id": 226071, "content": "只发少文字高逼格内容，不点赞其他人的内容。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 368806}, {"id": 226327, "content": "不做跟风狗，有自己的原则，该是什么就是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093821}, {"id": 231703, "content": "长得酷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 226072, "content": "多失恋多分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511342}, {"id": 226073, "content": "不在江湖，江湖却有我的传说", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741155}, {"id": 226329, "content": "混的比谁都好，朋友圈里啥都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858574}, {"id": 226074, "content": "话都反着说，不要随主流，你就觉得自己很酷了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092384}]}